            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> baharat</strong>,<strong> garam masala</strong> and<strong> ginger & garlic paste</strong> to the dish and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and<strong> chopped tomatoes </strong>with the <strong>chopped sweet potato </strong>and<strong> chicken stock</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and of<strong> pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Tip: Nestle the potatoes into the stock as much as you can!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1690219038033-x200.jpg",
