            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Bring to boil over a high heat then cover the dish with a lid</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 30-35 min or until the potatoes are tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Tip: Give everything a stir halfway through for evenly cooked potatoes!</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
