    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once your stew is ready, remove the dish from the oven and stir the <strong>spinach </strong>through, put the lid back on and let stand for 2-3 min until it has wilted – this is your <strong>Ethiopian-style chicken & sweet potato stew</strong></p>",
